All Classes

Class Description
Bee
The base class for all the different types of bees.
Bee.Role
The three roles
BeeHive
The BeeHive is the center of the world for the bees.
BeeMain
The main program for the bee simulation.

It is run on the command line with four arguments:

$ java BeeMain seconds drones nectar_workers pollen_workers
Drone
The male drone bee has a tough life.
FlowerField
The field of flowers that are ripe for the worker bees to gather the nectar and pollen resources.
Queen
The queen is the master of the bee hive and the only bee that is allowed to mate with the drones.
QueensChamber
The queen's chamber is where the mating ritual between the queen and her drones is conducted.
RandomBee
An unseeded random number generator that is suitable for generating random numbers in an inclusive range provided by the caller.
Worker
The female worker bee has the task of going to the flower field and collecting their assigned resource - nectar or pollen.
Worker.Resource
The resource the bee will be assigned to.
